<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>ARIA Corp. | ACCESS DENIED</title>
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Share+Tech+Mono&family=Orbitron:wght@900&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <style>
      :root {
        --bg: #030810;
        --accent2: #ff4444;
        --muted: #3a6b8a;
        --text: #a8d8ea;
      }
      * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }
      body {
        background: var(--bg);
        color: var(--text);
        font-family: "Share Tech Mono", monospace;
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 20px;
      }
      body::before {
        content: "";
        position: fixed;
        inset: 0;
        background-image:
          linear-gradient(rgba(255, 68, 68, 0.02) 1px, transparent 1px),
          linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255, 68, 68, 0.02) 1px, transparent 1px);
        background-size: 40px 40px;
      }
      .code {
        font-family: "Orbitron", monospace;
        font-weight: 900;
        font-size: clamp(4rem, 15vw, 9rem);
        color: var(--accent2);
        text-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(255, 68, 68, 0.5);
        position: relative;
        z-index: 2;
        animation: glitch 3s infinite;
      }
      @keyframes glitch {
        0%,
        92%,
        100% {
          text-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(255, 68, 68, 0.5);
        }
        93% {
          text-shadow:
            6px 0 #00d4ff,
            -6px 0 #ffcc00;
        }
        95% {
          text-shadow:
            -6px 0 #00d4ff,
            6px 0 #ffcc00;
        }
        97% {
          text-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(255, 68, 68, 0.5);
        }
      }
      .msg {
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        letter-spacing: 3px;
        color: var(--accent2);
        z-index: 2;
      }
      .sub {
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        color: var(--muted);
        letter-spacing: 1px;
        z-index: 2;
        text-align: center;
        line-height: 1.8;
      }
      .links {
        z-index: 2;
        display: flex;
        gap: 20px;
      }
      a {
        color: var(--muted);
        text-decoration: none;
        font-size: 0.78rem;
        letter-spacing: 2px;
        transition: color 0.2s;
      }
      a:hover {
        color: #00d4ff;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="code">403</div>
    <div class="msg">ACCESS DENIED</div>
    <div class="sub">
      현재 권한으로는 이 페이지에 접근할 수 없습니다.<br />
      당신의 역할:
      <strong style="color: #ff4444"
        ><%= user ? user.role.toUpperCase() : 'UNKNOWN' %></strong
      >
      · 필요 권한: <strong style="color: #ffcc00">ADMIN</strong><br /><br />
      어쩌면... 인증 토큰을 조작할 수 있지 않을까?
    </div>
    <div class="links">
      <a href="/dashboard">← 대시보드</a>
      <a href="/">홈으로</a>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
